data.description: Step into this beautifully renovated 5-bedroom, 4-bathroom single-family home, where every detail has been carefully curated to create a space that's not only stylish but also incredibly functional. The open layout eat-in kitchen has been transformed into a culinary haven with high-efficiency, top-of-the-line appliances. Whether you're a home chef or simply love to cook, this kitchen is sure to inspire your culinary creativity and make meal preparation a breeze. One of the standout features of this home is the electric fireplace for cozy nights. The custom closets add a touch of luxury and organization to every bedroom. These closets are designed to maximize storage space and streamline your daily routines. This home offers the utmost in convenience, as it's located within close proximity to transportation options, shops, and places of worship. It's a location that also provides accessibility to essential amenities and services. In conclusion, this single-family home represents the perfect blend of style, functionality, and convenience. With its new windows, custom closets, high-efficiency appliances, heated floors, energy star features and ideal location, it's a residence that caters to modern living. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional property your very own.
